---
title: Basil Pesto & Roasted Pumpkin Risoni with Lemon-Chilli Pangrattato & Crumbly Cheese
description: Risoni – the clever pasta that looks like rice – is the ideal ingredient in this warm bowl. With butternut
pumpkin and courgette, this dinner filled with goodness gets the welcome addition of crumbly cheese and
basil pesto to really raise the flavour stakes.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
